SELECT 
  mt.*,
  CASE WHEN mt."is_active" = true THEN 'active' ELSE 'not active' END AS "is_active_user"
FROM "salesforce_formula_integrations_tests"."user" AS mt
WHERE NOT mt._fivetran_deleted

SELECT 
  mt.*,
  CONCAT(mt."developer_name", mt."id") AS "developer_and_id"
FROM "salesforce_formula_integrations_tests"."user_role" AS mt
WHERE NOT mt._fivetran_deleted
